119
00:10:11,699 --> 00:10:14,379
Really? That's scary.

120
00:10:14,379 --> 00:10:15,740
I know.

121
00:10:29,610 --> 00:10:31,210
What a coincidence!

122
00:10:32,380 --> 00:10:34,749
- It's you.
- Yes.

123
00:10:34,749 --> 00:10:38,319
I was thinking about going to the design studio after having lunch.

124
00:10:38,319 --> 00:10:40,939
Why aren't you watching the shop?

125
00:10:40,939 --> 00:10:44,539
Are you... checking up on me?

126
00:10:44,539 --> 00:10:46,550
What do you mean?

127
00:10:47,040 --> 00:10:49,859
I'm going to buy ingredients.

128
00:10:49,859 --> 00:10:52,739
But doesn't HWC Roasters stock up on ingredients at the beginning or end of every month

129
00:10:52,739 --> 00:10:54,789
and also before and after New Year?

130
00:10:54,789 --> 00:10:58,079
You should be able to keep up with the number of ingredients.

131
00:10:58,079 --> 00:11:01,640
Or... were there many customers today?

132
00:11:03,770 --> 00:11:07,109
You figured out HWC Roasters completely.

133
00:11:07,109 --> 00:11:09,639
Do you want to set up a business?

134
00:11:09,639 --> 00:11:12,299
Not really.

135
00:11:12,299 --> 00:11:14,909
You better hurry. Lunchtime will be over soon.

136
00:11:14,909 --> 00:11:16,440
You're right.

137
00:11:19,220 --> 00:11:21,739
Isn't HWC Roasters that way?

138
00:11:21,739 --> 00:11:24,309
Today I'm craving something else. Do you want to come?

139
00:11:24,309 --> 00:11:25,790
Sure!

140
00:11:27,920 --> 00:11:29,859
How's school going?

141
00:11:29,859 --> 00:11:31,479
Pretty good.

142
00:11:31,479 --> 00:11:34,729
Oh, I just walked past where I used to live,

143
00:11:34,729 --> 00:11:37,269
and saw many police cars coming.

144
00:11:37,269 --> 00:11:40,150
Not my home, please. Please!

145
00:11:47,640 --> 00:11:50,979
It really is. Jin Yu Zhen,

146
00:11:50,979 --> 00:11:53,839
you better be safe.

147
00:11:53,839 --> 00:11:56,050
Sorry. I...

148
00:12:02,570 --> 00:12:04,909
Now you know you should apologize.

149
00:12:04,909 --> 00:12:06,549
I've been here so many times.

150
00:12:06,549 --> 00:12:08,479
This is my first time being mistaken for a thief.

151
00:12:08,479 --> 00:12:11,119
- You even called the police.
- Mom.

152
00:12:11,119 --> 00:12:12,759
Keep your mouth shut.

153
00:12:12,759 --> 00:12:14,539
This is between him and me.

154
00:12:14,539 --> 00:12:17,269
I didn't know that you were Shi Lei's mother.

155
00:12:17,269 --> 00:12:21,139
There was nobody else at home so when I heard something I couldn't help—

156
00:12:21,139 --> 00:12:24,969
I'm his mother. It is perfectly normal for me to have a key to this place.

157
00:12:24,969 --> 00:12:27,719
I even help clean and organize the place.

158
00:12:27,719 --> 00:12:30,670
How hilarious of you to call the police.

159
00:12:36,070 --> 00:12:38,289
No, wait. Lei Lei,

160
00:12:38,289 --> 00:12:39,859
I remember the one living with you was

161
00:12:39,859 --> 00:12:43,099
- a very cute young man.
- Oh,yes.

162
00:12:43,099 --> 00:12:45,939
How come it's this guy now?

163
00:12:45,939 --> 00:12:47,670
Ask him.

164
00:12:50,860 --> 00:12:54,520
It must be hard for you to live with this kind of person.

165
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:03,269
- What do you want?
- I will leave it to you. I will go to work now.

166
00:13:03,269 --> 00:13:06,499
- No, you—
- Where are you going?

167
00:13:06,499 --> 00:13:10,609
You can't leave without explanation.

168
00:13:21,320 --> 00:13:24,720
Auntie, I'm sorry. I haven't introduced myself properly.

169
00:13:24,720 --> 00:13:28,770
I'm the new person in charge of Jingcherng Metalwork and Design. My name is Jin Yu Zhen.

170
00:13:32,060 --> 00:13:34,080
Person in charge?

171
00:13:37,620 --> 00:13:39,440
So you're Lei Lei's boss?

172
00:13:39,440 --> 00:13:41,230
That's right.

173
00:13:43,420 --> 00:13:44,930
Why does he live here?

174
00:13:44,930 --> 00:13:46,790
The design studio was in a crisis.

175
00:13:46,799 --> 00:13:49,730
When I took over the company, I took over this house as well.

176
00:13:50,329 --> 00:13:53,319
Lei Lei, why didn't you tell me?

177
00:13:53,319 --> 00:13:55,089
So...

178
00:13:55,089 --> 00:13:57,450
He is the homeowner.

179
00:13:58,860 --> 00:14:00,730
That's right.

180
00:14:04,860 --> 00:14:07,339
I'm sorry. You're a young and capable boss.

181
00:14:07,339 --> 00:14:10,799
- I'm so sorry that I misunderstood you.
- Mom.

182
00:14:10,799 --> 00:14:14,149
- Lei Lei, will you get fired?
- I won't. Don't worry.

183
00:14:14,149 --> 00:14:17,699
Auntie, that's fine. Don't think too much. Maybe...

184
00:14:17,699 --> 00:14:19,769
Shi Lei has been so busy lately

185
00:14:19,769 --> 00:14:24,149
he forgot to tell you, and I also didn't introduce myself properly. It was my fault.

186
00:14:24,149 --> 00:14:26,639
Don't say that. You're such a young and capable boss.

187
00:14:26,639 --> 00:14:30,319
You even let Lei Lei live here. I'm so grateful. Thank you.

188
00:14:30,319 --> 00:14:34,779
Mom, he's not as good as you think.

189
00:14:34,779 --> 00:14:39,230
Shi Lei is very important to me. I should take care of him.

190
00:14:40,550 --> 00:14:43,400
- Boss, I've brought a lot of food with me.
- Mom!

191
00:14:43,400 --> 00:14:46,179
Lei Lei complains every time that he can't finish it all.

192
00:14:46,179 --> 00:14:48,559
Here you are. Do you want some?

193
00:14:48,559 --> 00:14:51,849
Auntie, sorry. I have to rush to the design studio.

194
00:14:51,849 --> 00:14:54,279
Have you eaten? Why don't you bring some to eat for lunch?

195
00:14:54,279 --> 00:14:55,460
That's fine. Don't bother.

196
00:14:55,460 --> 00:14:59,310
Exactly, Mom. He has a nickel allergy, so he can't just eat anything.

197
00:15:04,780 --> 00:15:06,869
Auntie, you both must have a lot to catch up on.

198
00:15:06,869 --> 00:15:09,119
How about I give Shi Lei some time off

199
00:15:09,119 --> 00:15:11,739
