200
00:15:11,739 --> 00:15:13,749
No, I'm good.

201
00:15:13,749 --> 00:15:16,309
Otherwise, he will blame me for having his pay docked.

202
00:15:16,310 --> 00:15:19,529
Auntie, don't worry. He just finished a really big project.

203
00:15:19,529 --> 00:15:22,199
He has also worked enough hours. It's a good idea for him to take some rest.

204
00:15:22,199 --> 00:15:24,120
His pay won't be docked.

205
00:15:26,100 --> 00:15:28,620
You're a great kid indeed.

206
00:15:30,770 --> 00:15:35,109
Mom, I can keep you company in the afternoon, but you may not be able to stay here tonight.

207
00:15:35,109 --> 00:15:39,859
- Why?
- Because we have a rule consisting of five things, the last of which says—

208
00:15:39,859 --> 00:15:42,210
Please rest assured and stay here.

209
00:15:43,600 --> 00:15:45,320
Thank you.

210
00:15:55,120 --> 00:15:58,420
My great team leader, what time is it now?

211
00:16:01,080 --> 00:16:02,609
Almost three o'clock.

212
00:16:02,609 --> 00:16:06,110
Almost three o'clock. You had a long lunch break.

213
00:16:06,110 --> 00:16:07,659
My mom came.

214
00:16:07,659 --> 00:16:11,310
I just helped her settle. Don't overreact.

215
00:16:12,400 --> 00:16:15,079
Big Bro Lei, your mom prepared a lot this time.

216
00:16:15,079 --> 00:16:17,310
- Yes, she was afraid—
- Will you listen to me?

217
00:16:20,680 --> 00:16:23,059
