218
00:16:23,060 --> 00:16:25,859
He only came here at noon and handed something off before leaving.

219
00:16:25,859 --> 00:16:27,809
I'll tell you what, the point is that he was weird.

220
00:16:27,810 --> 00:16:31,210
He seemed absent-minded, which I thought was a big problem.

221
00:16:31,810 --> 00:16:35,859
Maybe he's coming up with a new proposal just like this time.

222
00:16:35,859 --> 00:16:39,750
Maybe he's working on something private? Or he's dating someone?

223
00:16:39,750 --> 00:16:41,069
Aren't you overthinking this?

224
00:16:41,069 --> 00:16:45,300
It's not impossible. I'll tell you what, please be on high alert, okay?

225
00:16:52,340 --> 00:16:55,609
Please be on high alert, okay?

226
00:16:57,640 --> 00:16:59,220
Big Bro Lei.

227
00:17:00,430 --> 00:17:01,910
Okay.

228
00:17:08,790 --> 00:17:11,299
Shop Manager, why is it called Wan Wan?

229
00:17:11,299 --> 00:17:13,669
I named it. Don't you like it?

230
00:17:13,669 --> 00:17:15,999
Have you ever asked if it likes it?

231
00:17:15,999 --> 00:17:17,610
Right?

232
00:17:17,610 --> 00:17:18,720
Let me ask you then.

233
00:17:18,729 --> 00:17:22,850
Why am I wiping the table while you're playing with the cat?

234
00:17:25,300 --> 00:17:29,510
Why? Why? Why?

235
00:17:32,500 --> 00:17:34,710
Isn't that...

236
00:17:36,549 --> 00:17:38,380
Let's go.

237
00:17:41,090 --> 00:17:42,600
What's going on?

238
00:17:43,109 --> 00:17:45,930
I want to ask if I can borrow HWC Roasters.

239
00:17:47,060 --> 00:17:48,840
Is it about work?

240
00:17:49,470 --> 00:17:50,750
Yes.

241
00:18:04,610 --> 00:18:06,100
Did you get off work?

242
00:18:06,920 --> 00:18:09,379
Why did the shop close early today?

243
00:18:09,379 --> 00:18:13,110
It closed early because we're out of limited ingredients.

244
00:18:16,280 --> 00:18:18,080
Are you hungry?

245
00:18:19,710 --> 00:18:24,110
Because you said, you won't buy ingredients to cook at home.

246
00:18:25,840 --> 00:18:28,919
Then let's buy some for today together.

247
00:18:28,919 --> 00:18:30,480
Okay!

248
00:18:34,530 --> 00:18:37,279
Have you prepared for the metalwork course?

249
00:18:38,550 --> 00:18:41,020
Not yet.

250
00:18:41,020 --> 00:18:43,340
